description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of the site to provide new buildings ranging from 3 to 10 storeys in height comprising 118 residential units including affordable housing (Use Class C3), and 2,282m2 of flexible commercial floorspace (Use Classes A1-A4/B1/D1/D2), together with associated car parking, open space, landscaping and infrastructure works.
